description: Loads the metadata for all the dependent database objects of the parent object. This operation uses your project's Amazon S3 bucket as a metadata cache to improve performance.

parameters.name: MigrationProjectIdentifier
parameters.description: The migration project name or Amazon Resource Name (ARN).

parameters.name: SelectionRules
parameters.description: A value that specifies the database objects to import.

parameters.name: Origin
parameters.description: Whether to load metadata to the source or target database.

nested_items.name: RequestIdentifier
nested_items.description: The identifier for the import operation.
